      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone looking for a solid value. While the engine and transmission are running well, the exterior shows some noticeable clear coat peeling and a few minor door dings consistent with its age. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and the driver's seat shows significant wear, but all electronics and the air conditioning are fully functional. It has been regularly maintained, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the coming months. It\u2019s an honest car that gets the job done without any hidden surprises.",
      "price": 19500.0,
